    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional, collector-grade E36 M3. This example is powered by the S52 3.2L inline-six, featuring a fully serviced VANOS system and a precise ZF 5-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains structurally pristine with no subframe fatigue, retaining its factory-calibrated suspension geometry and limited-slip differential. Every body panel retains its original VIN tag, and the exterior finish shows zero evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. Inside, the Nappa leather 'Vader' seats are supple with intact bolsters. Mechanically optimized with a documented cooling system overhaul and fresh bushings, this M3 provides a direct, analog connection to the road with surgical throttle response and a linear power band.",
      "price": 46500.0,
